    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Maps in which aerial distribution is shown by distinctive colors or tints; most geological, soil, and political maps are of this type.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000025071/Harrod's Librarians' Glossary (1984)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Mapas en los que la distribución aérea se muestra con colores o tintes distintivos; la mayor parte de los mapas geológicos, terrestres y políticos son de este tipo.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
